## Workflow

Read the smallest relevant reference set for the task:
- Business flow or project method reuse: read [Business Methods](./references/business-methods.md), then the related business patterns
- API, generated layer, routes, or types: read [Project Spec](./references/project-spec.md) and structure/API patterns
- Architecture, module boundary, or dependency changes: read [Project Overview](./references/project-overview.md) and [Modules](./references/modules.md)
- Utilities, config, middleware, or concurrency: read only the matching category pattern

Prefer current code and high-confidence project patterns; treat medium-confidence patterns as guidance. If evidence is missing, state the gap instead of inventing implementation details.

